    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Facilities for extracting the salt from seawater in order to produce fresh water, which is water with a very low content of dissolved salt, as opposed to brackish water or salt water.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051009/Fiorenza et al, Solar Powered Water Desalination Plant (2003)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Anlage für die Extraktion von Salz aus Meerwasser, um Süßwasser zu gewinnen, einem Typus von Wasser mit geringem Salzgehalt im Gegensatz zu Salz- oder Brackwasser.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
